17#ifndef PACKET_H
18#define PACKET_H
19
20#include <termios.h>
21
22#include <openssl/bn.h>
23#include <openssl/ec.h>
24#include <sys/signal.h>
25#include <sys/queue.h>
26
27struct kex;
28struct sshkey;
29struct sshbuf;
30struct session_state; /* private session data */
31
32#include "dispatch.h" /* typedef, DISPATCH_MAX */
33
34struct key_entry {
35 TAILQ_ENTRY(key_entry) next;
36 struct sshkey *key;
37};
38
39struct ssh {
40 /* Session state */
41 struct session_state *state;
42
43 /* Key exchange */
44 struct kex *kex;
45
46 /* cached local and remote ip addresses and ports */
47 char *remote_ipaddr;
48 int remote_port;
49 char *local_ipaddr;
50 int local_port;
51 char *rdomain_in;
52
53 /* Optional preamble for log messages (e.g. username) */
54 char *log_preamble;
55
56 /* Dispatcher table */
57 dispatch_fn *dispatch[DISPATCH_MAX];
58 /* number of packets to ignore in the dispatcher */
59 int dispatch_skip_packets;
60
61 /* datafellows */
62 int compat;
63
64 /* Lists for private and public keys */
65 TAILQ_HEAD(, key_entry) private_keys;
66 TAILQ_HEAD(, key_entry) public_keys;
67
68 /* Client/Server authentication context */
69 void *authctxt;
70
71 /* Channels context */
72 struct ssh_channels *chanctxt;
73
74 /* APP data */
75 void *app_data;
76};
77

79 u_char *, void *);
